1.20	Siegel_+_Gale	Siegel + Gale	Siegel+Gale is a global strategic branding firm that employs over 250 people, including strategists, designers, information architects, research analysts, digital specialists, writers, and account managers. The company was founded in 1969 by Alan Siegel and Robert Gale. Siegel remains at the firm as the Chairman. David Srere and Howard Belk act as Co-CEOs. Siegel+Gale is a part of Omnicom Group . The firm is headquartered in New York with offices in Los Angeles, San Francisco, London, Dubai, Shanghai, Beijing, and Hamburg. It serves a wide range of corporate, non-profit, and government clients. Its corporate tagline is “Simple is Smart.”	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/31/SGLogo.gif/120px-SGLogo.gif
